location: 1446 East Washington Bld., Los Angeles, CA 90021.
description: UGLAR: Evan Skrederstu, Christopher D. Brand, Steve Martinez. This mural is a portrait of UGLAR member Jose A. Lopez wearing a traditional Mayan headdress (that of his ancestry). A second abstracted profile of his face represents his spiritual self. Commissioned by Box Eight Studios. Photo © Ian Robertson-Salt
